	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe you could put electrical tape (or anything thin, easily removed, and nonconductive) over cart pins 45/15 to isolate the audio path instead. Then there's no risk at all. (A game that relies on cart IRQs won't work, so pick something that doesn't use MMC3)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


